The paper discusses an end-to-end deep reinforcement learning approach for long-range navigation in unstructured environments, specifically cities. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of visual processing and Google StreetView also suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing for goal specification, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL).
